House of Representatives ad-hoc committee investigating the legality of the Special Presidential Investigation Panel (SPIP) on Thursday threatened to arrest members of the panel if they fail to appear before the committee on May 8, 2018. Those expected to appear before the ad-hoc committee are: Okoi Obono-Obla, chairman; Akinbola Adeniran, SPIP secretary; Salihu Abubakar, Obinna Ogwuegbu,…